comment: Wood (CHA) sets the screen on Griffin (LAC) and firms up his position upon contact.
Griffin (LAC) cleanly strips the ball from Batum (CHA).
Wood (CHA) makes incidental contact with Griffin (LAC) that does not affect his ability to control the loose ball.
Jordan (LAC) and Lamb (CHA) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Griffin (LAC) and Williams (CHA) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Walker (CHA) is not in a legal guarding position at the time of the contact with Griffin (LAC) on the driving shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a blocking foul on Walker (CHA) is confirmed.
Wood (CHA) sets the screen on Paul (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Walker (CHA) and Paul (LAC) briefly engage and separate on the perimeter.
Batum (CHA) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent but the shot by Paul (LAC) is imminent.
Rivers (LAC) makes contact with Walker's (CHA) body that affects his shot attempt in transition.
Lamb (CHA) makes contact with Redick (LAC) that affects his FOM off ball.
Jordan (LAC) sets the screen on Batum (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] LHH shows Jordan (LAC) never fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Batum (CHA) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Griffin (LAC) that affects his post shot attempt.
Jordan (LAC) makes contact with the ball after it hits the rim and is outside of the imaginary cylinder.
[Observable in enhanced video] Lamb (CHA) moves his pivot foot heel to toe.
Redick (LAC) makes contact to Lamb's (CHA) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Paul (LAC) sets the screen on Williams (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Williams (CHA) maintains legal guarding position on Griffin (LAC) in the post.
Jordan (LAC) makes marginal contact with Walker (CHA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Williams (CHA) has his heel in the restricted area and does not obtain a legal guarding position at the time of the contact with Griffin (LAC).
[Observable in enhanced video] Williams (CHA) and Jordan (LAC) enter the paint area prior to the free throw being released.
Williams (CHA) and Jordan (LAC) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Wood (CHA) sets the screen on Paul (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Paul (LAC) makes marginal contact with Walker (CHA) after he receives the inbound pass.
[Observable in enhanced video] Walker (CHA) moves his pivot foot.
Lamb (CHA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Paul (LAC) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Paul (LAC) commits a take foul on Walker (CHA).
[Observable in enhanced video] Jordan (LAC) and Williams (CHA) enter the paint area prior to the free throw being released.
LHH shows Griffin (LAC) grab Williams' (CHA) jersey and affect his ability to rebound.
LHH shows Williams (CHA) make contact with Griffin's (LAC) face that affects his ability to rebound.
Williams (CHA) commits a take foul on Griffin (LAC).
